                "detects": "Monitor changes to cloud-based directory services and identity tenants, especially regarding the addition of new federated identity providers. In Okta environments, the event system.idp.lifecycle.create will trigger on the creation of an identity provider, while sign-ins from a third-party identity provider will create the event user.authentication.auth_via_IDP.",
